name: TSG : Viper In Vanilla Street #1
description: Vanilla street in Strange Garden no : 0002 (Binary Garden) is famous for being the home of many outlaws, some even come from the other strange gardens making this street almost lawless. However all of these outlaws answer to one man, his name is Viper. They respect him and his words are the law in these street (Viper is the stranger in binary garden, Strangers are unique people picked by 'The System' to keep order in The Strange Gardens).
